FBIS3-23347 "jptot013__l94028" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 24 March 1994 LATIN AMERICA MEXICO `Pacifist' Writer Arrested for Killing Candidate Colosio Attorney General Appoints Special Prosecutor PA2403140994 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 1210 GMT 24 Mar 94 PA2403140994 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Attorney General Diego Valadez said he has been specifically instructed by President Carlos Salinas de Gortari to direct the investigation. The president of the republic appointed (Santiago Unate Laborde), one of Luis Donaldo Colosio's close collaborators, to be special prosecutor in charge of investigating the attack's details.
